{
 "prompt": "A sleek frosted glass dropper bottle with a golden cap, holding shimmering amber serum, A futuristic, abstract art gallery space with geometric light patterns, Extreme long shot of the product floating ethereally in the center of the abstract space, surrounded by dynamic geometric light patterns, Hard/High Contrast lighting, Hasselblad X2D, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "surreal, grand", "color": "deep blues, vibrant purples, amber", "lighting": "sharp, high contrast" }
}
```
